translation[9]{c,v,t}:
  30,42,Zamin mein chal phir ker dekho to sahi kay aglon ka anjam kiya hua. Jin mein aksar log mushrik thay
  30,43,Pus aap apna rukh uss sachay aur seedhay deen ki taraf hi rakhen qabal iss kay kay woh din aajaye jiss ka tal jana Allah Taalaa ki taraf say hai hi nahi uss din sab mutafarriq ho jayen gay
  30,44,Kufur kerney walon per unn kay kufur ka wabaal hoga aur nek kaam kerney walay apni hi aaram gaah sanwaar rahey hain
  30,45,Takay Allah Taalaa unhen apnay fazal say jaza dey jo eman laye aur nek aemaal kiyey woh kafiron ko dost nahi rakhta hai
  30,46,Uss ki nishaniyon mein say khushkhabriyan denay wali hawaon ko chalana bhi hai iss liye kay tumhen apni rehmat say lutf andoz keray aur iss liye kay uss kay hukum say kashtiyan chalen aur iss liye kay uss kay fazal ko tum dhondo aur iss liye kay tum shukar guzari kero
  30,47,Aur hum ney aap say pehlay bhi apnay rasoolon ko unn ki qom ki taraf bheja woh unn kay pass deleelen laye. Phir hum ney gunehgaaron say intiqam liya. Hum per momino ki madad kerna lazim hai
  30,48,Allah Taalaa hawayen chalata hai woh abar ko uthati hain phir Allah Taalaa apni mansha kay mutabiq ussay aasman mein phela deta hai aur uss kay tukray tukray ker deta hai phir aap dekhtay hain kay uss kay andar say qatray nikaltay hain aur jinhen Allah chahata hai unn bandon per qoh pani barsata hai to woh khush khush ho jatay hain
  30,49,Yaqeen manna kay barish unn per barasney say pehlay pehlay to woh na umeed ho rahey thay
  30,50,Pus aap rehmat-e-elahee kay aasaar dekhen kay zamin ki maut kay baad kiss tarah Allah Taalaa ussay zinda ker deta hai? Kuch shak nahi kay wohi murdon ko zinda kerney wala hai aur woh her her cheez per qadir hai